results.name: The second infinite sequence of positive integers such that a(n) = A037445(a(1)+a(2)+...+a(n)) for all n>=1 (see also A260085).
comment: The second after A260085 infinitary analog of A259935 (see comment there). Using Falcao's method (2015) one can prove that such an infinite sequence exists.
results.author: _Vladimir Shevelev_, Jul 17 2015
